OK that'll work, the line was intended to go on both sides of Grimlock and
pin him to the ground.

A diaoriented Switchblade watched as one of the blades was bit in half. the
laser line disipated as the other blade bounced off the ground. The big bot
was alot tougher than Switchblade had origionally anticipated. It had
already taken two missles solidly to it's body and still got up to fight.
With his senses messed up he was having trouble aiming so he thought it was
better to remain perched on the building and let the others inflict some
damage.
